{
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "轻量的 Scoop 应用搜索工具，支持从桶中快速检索应用程序并以格式化表格展示结果",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/bright-angel/scoop-searchx",
    "license": "unknown",
    "url": "https://github.com/bright-angel/scoop-searchx/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.0.zip#/scoop-searchx.zip",
    "hash": "sha256:3CC591CA57A083C601B24806C086FFFA1180955F8B9A1FF33735BD985F712056",
    "extract_dir": "scoop-searchx-1.0.0",
    "suggest": {
        "uv": "uv"
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\scoop-searchx.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0', '@uv run python \"scoop-searchx.py\" %*', '@popd' -Encoding Ascii",
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\ss.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0', '@uv run python \"scoop-searchx.py\" %*', '@popd' -Encoding Ascii"

    ],
    "post_install": [
        "uv venv \"$dir\\.venv\"",
        "uv pip install -r \"$dir\\requirements.txt\" --python \"$dir\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe\""
    ],
    "bin": [
        "scoop-searchx.bat",
        "ss.bat"
    ],
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: Scoop 辅助工具",
        "【主要功能】: 从 Scoop 桶中快速检索应用程序，格式化表格展示搜索结果",
        "【适用场景】: 日常 Scoop 应用查找、桶内应用浏览",
        "【技术特点】: 基于 Python + PrettyTable 开发，轻量简洁",
        "【注意事项】: 项目仓库已不存在，当前版本为最后可用版本"
    ]
}
